;br /&gt;Tara Brown - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/cursed-book-1-devils-roses/id591633987?mt=11"&gt;Cursed (Book 1 of the Devil's Roses)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;M. Leighton - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/madly-book-1-madly-series/id449627235?mt=11"&gt;Madly&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Rachel Higginson - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/love-and-decay/id677676579?mt=11"&gt;Love and Decay&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;Teen Fiction&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chanda Hahn - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/unenchanted/id493267725?mt=11"&gt;UnEnchanted&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;GJ Walker-Smith - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/saving-wishes/id648553980?mt=11"&gt;Saving Wishes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Quinn Loftis - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/prince-wolves-book-1-grey/id462923655?mt=11"&gt;Prince of Wolves&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Amy Miles - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/forbidden/id488515594?mt=11"&gt;Forbidden&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tracie Puckett - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/the-new-girl/id595759933?mt=11"&gt;The New Girl&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Jessica Sorenson - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/fallen-star-fallen-star-series/id492235814?mt=11"&gt;The Fallen Star&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Julia Templeton - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/the-deepest-cut/id476346942?mt=11"&gt;The Deepest Cut&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Penelope Fletcher - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/glamour-rae-wilder-1/id398436739?mt=11"&gt;Glamour&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Kira Saito - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/bound/id485729831?mt=11"&gt;Bound&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Shelly Crane - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/significance/id604300735?mt=11"&gt;Significance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Erica Stevens - &lt;a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/kindred/id550250187?mt=11"&gt;Kindred&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Melanie Nilles -&amp;nbsp; &lt;a href="https://itune